<reference id="topic" xml:lang="en-us">
<title><keyword>topic</keyword></title>
<shortdesc>The &lt;<keyword>topic</keyword>> element is the top-level DITA
element for a single-subject topic or article. Other top-level DITA elements
that are more content-specific are &lt;<keyword>concept</keyword>>, &lt;<keyword>task</keyword>>,
and &lt;<keyword>reference</keyword>>.</shortdesc>
<prolog><metadata>
