<indexterm>topic</indexterm></keywords>
</metadata></prolog>
<refbody>
<section> <p>To support applications that are namespace-aware, DITA DTDs and
Schemas provide the following fixed namespaced declarations for topic, and
for topic-level elements derived from topic: <pre>
ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.0" 
xmlns:ditaarch="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/" 
</pre> In DTDs, the <q>ditaarch</q> prefix is parameterized to enable future
specialization.</p> <p>All DITA elements take the <codeph>xmlns=""</codeph> fixed
attribute, which puts them into the null namespace by default.  This attribute
is applied via the %global-atts; group.</p>        </section>
